{"tid":1676551,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【科技台】天價肌肉萎縮症藥物大賣，瑞士諾華製藥利潤超預期","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T14:02:02.000Z","uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"918b8ade516dc1f8ccf5ee8707d4ec0385a0d60a","tid":1676551,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-22/novartis-earnings-outlook-improves-for-third-time-this-year\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-10-22%2Fnovartis-earnings-outlook-improves-for-third-time-this-year&d=udS8qETdHRHoQIkzJVaZjogmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=1890a35d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-10-22/novartis-earnings-outlook-improves-for-third-time-this-year</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qtxasset.com/styles/breakpoint_xl_880px_w/s3/fiercepharma/1571756207/Vialandbox_1558464320138-HR.jpg/Vialandbox_1558464320138-HR.jpg?u0jFQG1r0sDWt7MGnVvp7LDCqbZuOMdn&amp;itok=x8QHY7pL\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqtxasset.com%2Fstyles%2Fbreakpoint_xl_880px_w%2Fs3%2Ffiercepharma%2F1571756207%2FVialandbox_1558464320138-HR.jpg%2FVialandbox_1558464320138-HR.jpg%3Fu0jFQG1r0sDWt7MGnVvp7LDCqbZuOMdn%26itok%3Dx8QHY7pL&h=55ca4824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全球最昂貴藥物Zolgensma在今年5月推出後，高藥價不僅沒有對買氣造成影響，反而還帶動母公司諾華第三季獲利傳出捷報。基於Zolgensma銷售強勁，該藥廠已調高今年全年財測。<br />\n<br />\n諾華周二（22日）公布第三季財報，獲利年增8％到20.4億美元、營收也增長10％到121.7億美元，兩者均優於市場預期。該製藥大廠表示，上季獲利亮眼，治療幼兒罕見遺傳疾病的Zolgensma厥功甚偉。它在該季銷售高達1.6億美元，超出外界預期的9,800萬美元。上季是它推出後的首季全季銷售表現。<br />\n<br />\n隸屬一次性基因療法，專門治療幼兒神經肌肉疾病的Zolgensma在5月底推出後，單劑要價高達210萬美元。由於價格不斐，也引發外界質疑政府與醫療保險公司是否有能力供應這類昂貴藥物。"},{"pid":"a7bc20d64af2ac708f35a00a25d10e958ba770fd","tid":1676551,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3959fb28c38f0342cf4e9a25bf00e1e7d60ad1","tid":1676551,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9aaa78498d221d3ff0ba26808ece0ca73820a3","tid":1676551,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rG9c5Um.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrG9c5Um.gif&h=4ad4d108&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}